# GitHub account: always `solzito148`

In this repository (`cpm`), **always use the `solzito148` GitHub account** for git and `gh`. Never push as `msanes_meli`.

## Before push

```bash
gh auth status | grep -A1 'solzito148' | grep 'Active account: true'
```

If inactive: `gh auth switch --user solzito148`

## Remote

- Origin: `https://github.com/solzito148/cpm.git`
- Prefer HTTPS push (SSH may still use `msanes_meli` on this machine).
- If SSH push fails with "Permission denied to msanes_meli", retry with HTTPS origin or `git push https://github.com/solzito148/cpm.git main`.
